r^{-1}\hat{\mathbf e}_\theta[f] = r^{-1}\dfrac{\partial}{\partial \theta}[f] = r(6\sin \theta \cos \theta + 4\cos \theta \sin \theta) = 10r\sin \theta \cos \theta; \tag{7}
